Overview

The Dashboard page on Phoenix Hub provides an at-a-glance view of key information and quick access to essential functions for managing your digital assets on Stellar.

Key Sections

  1. Current Prices
    • XLM Price: Displays the current market price of Stellar (XLM).
    • PHO Price: Shows the current market price of Phoenix (PHO).
  2. Portfolio Overview
    • Quick summary of your portfolio's value, including holdings in XLM, PHO, and other assets.
  3. Buy Crypto
    • Provides a straightforward option to purchase more cryptocurrency directly from the dashboard. (Through our Partner Kado).

Features

  • Real-Time Price Updates: Stay updated with the latest price changes for XLM and PHO.
  • Easy Access to Purchases: Quickly buy more cryptocurrency without navigating away from the dashboard.
  • Transaction Monitoring: Keep track of your recent transactions to manage your portfolio effectively.

Usage Tips

  • Regularly check the Dashboard for the latest price updates and portfolio performance.
  • Utilize the "Buy Crypto" feature for quick acquisitions without the need to go through a centralized exchange.

For more detailed information and advanced functionalities, explore other sections like Swap, Pools, and Trade History.
